## Installation Pypi
```
# Requires Python >=3.6
pip install GluonixDesigner

# Start Application
Gluonix
#or
GluonixDesigner
```

## Installation Git
```
# Requires Python >=3.6
git clone https://github.com/nucleonautomation/Gluonix-Designer.git

# Start Application
cd Gluonix-Designer
python Designer.py
```

## Requirements
```
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

